title: My Little Pony: Friendship is Magic S4E01 & S4E2 Princess Tw
description: In this new episode, Twilight is busy adjusting to her new wings and her new role as a princess! Just then before the Summer Sun Celebration, Princess Celestia and Luna go missing. The Everfree Forest starts to take over Equestria without them. It's up to the six friends to discover who is causing all this chaos and along the way, discover the hidden secrets of the Elements Of Harmony.
